  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1006">
<l>ētam peruñcelvan tāṉṟuvvāṉ ṟakkārkkoṉ</l>
<l>ṟīta liyalpilā tāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who enjoys not (his riches) nor relieves the wants of the worthy is a disease to his wealth.</l>
            </lg>
